{"name": "odoo-addon-shopinvader-search-engine-update", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-shopinvader-search-engine-update", "version": "16.0.1.0.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-shopinvader-search-engine", "odoo"], "summary": "Shopinvader: Mark product binding to export on product update", "upload_time": 1713779557}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Alpha-red.png\n    :alt: Alpha\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-shopinvader%2Fodoo--shopinvader-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader\n    :target: https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/tree/16.0/shopinvader_search_engine_update\n    ```\n---\n\n# Shopinvader Search Engine Update\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:40b421b09321c95c81cd43cb3a7bb41555ecf9d1984cb54966809b15436ee4f0\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }}\n\nThis module extends the functionality of the\n`shopinvader_search_engine` to mark the information exported to the\nsearch engine as to be recomputed when the product data are updated.\n\n:::{IMPORTANT}\nThis is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.\nOnly for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.\n[More details on development status](https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status)\n:::\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Use Cases / Context\n\nWhen you update your product data and this information is exposed by the\nsearch engine, you expect to see your changes applied into the search\nengine as soon as possible.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues/new?body=module:%20shopinvader_search_engine_update%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Laurent Mignon <mailto:laurent.mignon@acsone.eu> (<https://www.acsone.eu>)\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is part of the [shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader](https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/tree/16.0/shopinvader_search_engine_update) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_update.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_update.models.product_product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_update.models..product_product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_update.models.product_template", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.shopinvader_search_engine_update.models..product_template", "pro